      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Design a platform that enables internal teams to train, deploy, and operate ML models at scale.\n\nThis is not a consumer AI product. It’s an internal ML/AI platform used by:\n        •        Data scientists\n        •        Backend engineers\n        •        Product teams integrating inference into production systems\n\nThe platform must support:\n        •        Batch training\n        •        Online inference\n        •        Model versioning and rollback\n        •        Multi-team isolation\n        •        Cost controls\n\nAssume:\n        •        Kubernetes is already the company’s orchestration layer\n        •        Teams range from very mature ML users to first-time adopters\n        •        Leadership is worried about “runaway GPU spend” and unreliable models in prod",
      "fontSize": 15.615624999999987,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design a platform that enables internal teams to train, deploy, and operate ML models at scale.\n\nThis is not a consumer AI product. It’s an internal ML/AI platform used by:\n        •        Data scientists\n        •        Backend engineers\n        •        Product teams integrating inference into production systems\n\nThe platform must support:\n        •        Batch training\n        •        Online inference\n        •        Model versioning and rollback\n        •        Multi-team isolation\n        •        Cost controls\n\nAssume:\n        •        Kubernetes is already the company’s orchestration layer\n        •        Teams range from very mature ML users to first-time adopters\n        •        Leadership is worried about “runaway GPU spend” and unreliable models in prod",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ffq5xnUC_yHPMzzkfO3gk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -823.2680631066356,
      "y": 123.42510083902772,
      "width": 1789.9345408739678,
      "height": 3268.285235119692,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5n",
