      "updated": 1768513685481,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    An average inference can handle up to 32 threads per GPU.\n    An average inference will have 4 GPUs.\n    Max Concurrent Threads: Max RPS( 20,000 ) * Max Model Response Time(60 seconds) = 1,200,000\n    Avg Concurrent Threads: Avg RPS( 2,000 ) * Avg Model Response Time(30 seconds) = 60,000\n    Max Inference Data in KB per second: Avg Data size(10 KB) * Max RPS( 20,000 ) = 200,000Kb or 200Mb/sec\n    Avg Inference Data in KB per second: Avg Data size(10 KB) * Avg RPS( 2,000 )  = 20Mb/sec\n    An average inference can handle (threads per GPU) * (GPUs) = 128 threads concurrently.\n    The max number of inferences will be 1,200,000(concurrent threads) / 128(max threads per) = 9,000+\n    The avg number of GPUs needed will be 60,000(concurrent threads) / 32(threads per GPU) = 1,800+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    An average inference can handle up to 32 threads per GPU.\n    An average inference will have 4 GPUs.\n    Max Concurrent Threads: Max RPS( 20,000 ) * Max Model Response Time(60 seconds) = 1,200,000\n    Avg Concurrent Threads: Avg RPS( 2,000 ) * Avg Model Response Time(30 seconds) = 60,000\n    Max Inference Data in KB per second: Avg Data size(10 KB) * Max RPS( 20,000 ) = 200,000Kb or 200Mb/sec\n    Avg Inference Data in KB per second: Avg Data size(10 KB) * Avg RPS( 2,000 )  = 20Mb/sec\n    An average inference can handle (threads per GPU) * (GPUs) = 128 threads concurrently.\n    The max number of inferences will be 1,200,000(concurrent threads) / 128(max threads per) = 9,000+\n    The avg number of GPUs needed will be 60,000(concurrent threads) / 32(threads per GPU) = 1,800+",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
